<li id="fn:lol">
<p>I'm trying really hard to not make a terrible pun involving (manic-)depressed cubic equations and polar representations&#160;<a href="#fnref:lol" rev="footnote" title="Jump back to footnote 1 in the text">&#8617;</a></p>
</li>
</ol>
